title: CAKE-BNB LP x30 restructure
body:
We should restructure a bit with the pools, currently:

CAKE-BNB FLIP x20 
BUSD-BNB FLIP x8
ADA-BNB FLIP x3
BAND-BNB FLIP x3
DOT-BNB FLIP x3
EOS-BNB FLIP x3
LINK-BNB FLIP x3

NEW PROPOSAL:
CAKE-BNB FLIP x30
BUSD-BNB FLIP x3
ADA-BNB FLIP x2
BAND-BNB FLIP x2
DOT-BNB FLIP x2
EOS-BNB FLIP x2
LINK-BNB FLIP x2

This wont make too much dramatic changes, and it will increase the incentive a lot for CAKE-BNB holders just by doing a smaller change that most likely wont lower the TVL (since the APYs for the other FLIPs are still way above market %).

VOTE YES IF YOU LIKE THE IDEA

VOTE NO IF YOU THINK ITS A BAD IDEA.
author: 0x3e8734Ec146C981E3eD1f6b582D447DDE701d90c
